{"tid":1650670,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"網傳香港警員申請移民 內政部：曾參加暴力組織者將拒絕申請","createTime":"2019-10-13T05:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T06:14:11.000Z","uid":144372,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"44b110014b04d0656ec9cfc695fcc42f2dd50061","tid":1650670,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:36:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/home/回應網傳香港警員申請移民-台灣稱將查核審視-044921469.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fhome%2F%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%A8%B1%E5%B0%87%E6%9F%A5%E6%A0%B8%E5%AF%A9%E8%A6%96-044921469.html&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=512cbdc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/home/回應網傳香港警員申請移民-台灣稱將查核審視-044921469.html</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣的內政部回應網上有傳聞指，大批香港警員攜同家屬申請移民到台灣，強調所有各類居留及定居的申請個案，移民署都會透過各種管道，進行安全查核及審視，確保將不法及犯罪，阻絕於境外。<br />\n內政部說，根據現行規定，港澳居民可以因為工作、投資、就學等理由，申請移民台灣，但如果申請人曾經有犯罪行為、危害國家利益、公共安全、公共秩序、參加或資助恐怖或暴力非法組織等，移民署將不會批准有關申請。<br />\n內政部又澄清，網上有傳聞用600萬台幣在台灣買樓就可以移民，是錯誤訊息。"},{"pid":"ff800803a25504142db481c92b02991bc0d57253","tid":1650670,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:37:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b51d886056038a063c2f5b0cb06d3e1f837f727c","tid":1650670,"uid":56627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T05:37:45.000Z","msg":"HK Police=暴力犯罪組織"},{"pid":"79117c711ea6d04f4a4e196498476a2aab62edd6","tid":1650670,"uid":99473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:07:40.000Z","msg":"連登仔又自欺欺人<br />\n義士都唔走得啦今次"},{"pid":"b2e611f911f6f3f366a4c829b7938a54fb2011b5","tid":1650670,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79117c711ea6d04f4a4e196498476a2aab62edd6","tid":1650670,"uid":99473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:07:40.000Z","msg":"連登仔又自欺欺人<br />\n義士都唔走得啦今次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:09:08.000Z","msg":"義士就去美國喇懵撚"},{"pid":"153d09c7e64ef425f05578525a9207d0f53e1b8b","tid":1650670,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:14:11.000Z","msg":"別讓香港警察跑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}